<section>
<section id="slide-org34d8b5a">
<h2 id="org34d8b5a">Fixed and manipulable rules</h2>
<ul>
<li>Fixed rules can't be altered by players</li>
<li>The choices available to each player are constant and known</li>

</ul>

</section>
</section>
<section>
<section id="slide-orgaa1ac64">
<h2 id="orgaa1ac64">Nim</h2>
